snippet.title: Oceaneers - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Craft. Float. Survive.
Wishlist OCEANEERS on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3052510/Oceaneers/

Oceaneers is a raft-crafting survival management adventure set on sinkable islands. 

Control a group of survivors to scavenge, harvest and craft your way to an island colony! Build expedition rafts, research contraptions to keep islands afloat, and create your own floating settlement.

#games #gaming #indiegame
